Shota, I went to a cram school and I'm not at home.

I managed to get into the school she wanted to go to

(I have to do my best too ...)

It's not the case when I'm playing too, I'm sorry ...
"I'm sorry. I'm not saying you can't play.
Playing as a distraction and stretching the wings is also

I think Shota went to cram school all the time during the summer vacation ...
"... Would you like to play with me?"

"So ... if you're just talking to someone ...
I wish I could help even a little …….
Even if Shota wasn't there ... that ... even if he came to play.
My husband was also busy with work and was away from home ...
"If you go to Shota Cram School,
I will be the only one in this large house ...
"That's why it's not annoying at all.
It's okay to come visit us anytime.
Is it okay to talk a little?
Do you call me Minori, not an aunt?
